  "steps": [
    "Login to http://github.com",
    "Click on &#34;Repositories&#34; a",
    "Click on &#34;New&#34; a",
    "Enter &#34;abe487&#34; (lowercase, please) for the &#34;Repository name&#34;. Click &#34;Initialize this repository with a README&#34; so it won&#39;t be empty. If you don&#39;t do this, then remove it and recreate.",
